descr: "A structured set of tests against a FHIR server implementation to determine compliance against the FHIR specification."

fields.name: autocreate
fields.descr: "Whether or not to implicitly create the fixture during setup. If true, the fixture is automatically created on each server being tested during setup, therefore no create operation is required for this fixture in the TestScript.setup section."

fields.name: autodelete
fields.descr: "Whether or not to implicitly delete the fixture during teardown. If true, the fixture is automatically deleted on each server being tested during teardown, therefore no delete operation is required for this fixture in the TestScript.teardown section."

fields.name: resource
fields.descr: "Reference to the resource (containing the contents of the resource needed for operations)."
